    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to check out this absolute beauty. It\u2019s seriously in incredible shape\u2014honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It\u2019s ready for a new home, and I promise you\u2019re going to love it as much as I do! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
