    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present an exemplary vehicle maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This specimen exhibits an immaculate exterior finish and a pristine interior cabin, mirroring its original showroom condition. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically flawless, this vehicle represents a rare acquisition opportunity for the sophisticated investor or enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality.",
