    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. It drives like a cloud and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as cherished. Seriously, you won't find one cleaner than this. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
