      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit with its high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells. The chassis is structurally sound with reinforced subframe mounts, ensuring optimal lateral stiffness. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Finished in pristine Carbon Black Metallic over Nappa leather, the factory geometry remains dialed for peak mechanical grip. A purist\u2019s example with zero parasitic draw or fluid seepage.",
